Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.65,0:01:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是鼬鼠丫頭\N在山上精神特別好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.89,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小操 翁爺爺在京都\N恐怕非常擔心你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在大阪有寫信給他\N沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.36,0:02:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 緋村你們的旅行\N為什麼這麼不順利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.17,0:02:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 在清水因為船故障\N而被趕上岸之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一直都用步行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肚子餓得不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往這邊走就到箱根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,箱根是很出名的溫泉鄉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過而不入太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是 去吃一頓飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後泡溫泉\N消除旅行的疲倦也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚就住在箱根吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.06,0:02:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.40,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十八話\N美術學生思念的女性\N箱根溫泉街的念愛騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好飽好飽 啊 好飽好飽\N再也吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房間與料理都最高級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.41,0:02:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這裏離東京就很近了\N偶爾就是應該享受一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.12,0:03:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 恕我失禮問個問題\N請問你們付帳沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這房間是最高級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 還有剩很多路費吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 劍心\N交給你保管的錢沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 我保管在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.94,0:03:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會劍心 你把錢搞丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…就是那個該不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還敢笑 快找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.43,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 客人們身無分文了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大掌櫃 糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀 你那邊也有爭執啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.04,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然來了一整團客人\N我們忙著招待不過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.54,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在人手不足 傷腦筋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大掌櫃 讓我工作付住宿費吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也要工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們劍心組是團結一心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粗活包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.16,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\N我可是京都出名的料理亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋的卷町操呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種工作我太熟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 大家加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對不對 不是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底還缺少什麼\N缺少什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃過飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 可能我們搞錯房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慘了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 等等呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她！就是她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呀 這就是天無絕人之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差點以為完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像還可以賺到東京的旅行費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.32,0:05:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我的疏忽…\N大家對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是劍心組哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到了終極的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.49,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不輸給那星星的永遠的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所尋求的答案！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.08,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流汗之後洗澡真享受\N太舒服了 太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.85,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 小操\N我家的劍心連累大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂 無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.19,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是你喊劍心是你家的\N真的好親密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不是 我沒那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.73,0:06:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你誤會了 小操\N我跟劍心還不是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就猜到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在那方面態度完全曖昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知他心裏是怎麼看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他\N又不像是對女人沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是另有喜歡的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是忘不了過去的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.88,0:06:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是年紀差太多\N沒有把阿薰當成女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.02,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你不用擔心我了\N反倒是你自己呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.56,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無所謂的\N不管蒼紫大人怎樣想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心意一輩子不變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏 可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色、色、色狼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准看！別過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 這是第四次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.68,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被緋村看見了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的好奇心太強了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種人應該處死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我絕不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在東京學習西洋畫的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫做東山龍三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是學畫的學生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.17,0:07:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這幾年我不斷為藝術是什麼\N這基本的問題而苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.01,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後 為了找出那答案\N我下定決心出來旅行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我還是找不出答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是過著空虛的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.39,0:08:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後我終於徹底喪失信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.06,0:08:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 一眼看到她時\N我才恍然大悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我而言 藝術是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就世上最美的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要描繪出終極之美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終極之美是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽不懂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單講\N就是你找到超級大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後 明知她在入浴中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太想把她的身影\N畫進這本素描簿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入浴中 不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦 不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解我的美麗的人\N世上只要有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人就足夠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了藝術 我必需畫你才行\N請你當我的模特兒吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.06,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道藝術是什麼\N但是你把我畫成畫是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完完全全…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在樂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她樂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛\N我是跟阿薰在一起的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一間要準備\N請你們快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被當奴隸差遣\N阿薰這時候卻偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰並不是在玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說\N她是為了藝術 藝術呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上最美麗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是頭一次被男人這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心從不誇獎我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知他是沒有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是神經太遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這種感覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 請快去菊之間吧\N那裏有團體客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.87,0:10:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒 畫得跟阿薰一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.98,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 小操\N他說這個只是草圖而已呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實有兩把刷子\N能把阿薰畫成大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我閉嘴 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你挺有實力的嘛\N對你刮目相看了 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是個空殼子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是真正的阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 難得畫那麼漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表看來確實是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這張畫\N沒有畫入最重要的心呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我看不見阿薰的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.03,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我愛上了阿薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愛上…小姐了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 畫著她的時候\N我忍不住想更瞭解她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 那時候我已經掉入愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是諷刺的是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這激熱的思念蒙蔽了我的雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰的心啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見阿薰的心之後\N恐怕連魔鬼都會逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 請跟我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.62,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話 我相信總有一天\N我一定能看清楚你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我的藝術完成之日！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼說 我也很為難…\N好傷腦筋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.03,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 阿薰已經有緋村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦 小操真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 菊之間在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.86,0:13:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所見 雖然不很順利\N但是小姐的心意很明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我潑你冷水\N你還是死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.44,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣\N我好不容易找到的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼呀！小伙子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我放棄阿薰 我不如去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.76,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 你要死是你的自由\N別選我們在的時候！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男子漢\N不可以輕易把自殺掛在嘴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.44,0:14:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你是男子漢 拜託你\N幫我想想辦法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人這樣要求\N身為男子漢是無法拒絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你乾脆幫幫他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.92,0:14:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別給我多嘴\N我最討厭惹上麻煩事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.46,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別叫別叫 我有個好主意\N耳朵湊過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.63,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小伙子 看在你夠熱誠\N我可以幫你的忙沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天日落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.74,0:14:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你能夠打中劍心一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.88,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我就負責撮合你與小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我從沒學過劍道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼此事當我沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 這是男人跟男人的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.23,0:14:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你還辦不到\N就要勇敢忘記我們小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了吧 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.87,0:15:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 左之助\N我也是男人 絕不食言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.34,0:15:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了得到阿薰的心\N完成我的藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場決鬥我一定要贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記說一句話了\N別看劍心呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可是幕末時候\N在京都連新撰組都會害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱為斬人拔刀齊的男人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就小心行事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟對手是斬人拔刀齊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好笑了\N聽到是斬人拔刀齊就怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣那傢伙應該醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們別把我的竹刀\N拿去做那種用途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正他會很快就死心\N拿來還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.98,0:15:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小伙子…不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的去偷襲緋村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得早點做完去準備晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加快一下節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是幕末時候的殺人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正面攻他是絕對沒勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要在背後出其不意偷襲\N賭上我的一線希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.35,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才好像聽到人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的去偷襲劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知是不自量力\N還是不要命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的竹刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…百合之間確實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿劍 這邊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿劍 快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.07,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等著瞧吧 阿薰 我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天總感到身邊有奇怪的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是我累了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟工作了一整天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 無法用手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那位學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這樣自作主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我沒告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你放心吧\N以他的身手呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算花上一百年時間\N也不可能打倒緋村的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快超過限定時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心的是龍三郎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他受重傷就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他應該死心了\N不過為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是去找他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話 找緋村最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.44,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心應該上山\N採集晚餐要用的山菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也一起去 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.86,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 我採到這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來什麼事也沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說得沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都聚在這裏是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還沒放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的竹刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助這到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的 劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.16,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰別過去 那是雀蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你救那個學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.49,0:19:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好只是手臂受傷\N你別太讓人擔心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別太沮喪啦 小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來…原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰的心中\N充滿了對緋村的情意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那美麗是愛著緋村的心\N的一種表現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.59,0:20:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能畫 現在我能畫出來\N畫下阿薰的真實模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.44,0:20:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才能清楚發現\N活下去的藝術之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.21,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 龍三郎還有\N藝術這條很棒的道路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也祝阿薰你幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 這是送給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.82,0:20:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見 阿薰\N各位也保重 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比阿薰漂亮的美女很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 你話太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.50,0:21:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再工作兩三天\N就可以回東京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面就是東海官道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直走就到東京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操你果然是想念京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.29,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 我一直很在意\N那張畫畫了什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.29,0:21:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦 我想回到東京以後\N再打開來看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小氣了 讓我看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.96,0:21:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也好想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能看一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說主題是女神的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像不像我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不看了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 彌彥 我們先趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然這麼慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.77,0:22:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什、什麼 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑死人了 還說是女神的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助\N這樣講對阿薰太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村也是 你自己還不是笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我笑得肚子好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰果然是那種人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.12,0:22:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們笑什麼笑啊！不要跑！

